# [ROLL](../wg/roll.html)

## Summary

The ROLL Working Group held an interim meeting to discuss the status of active drafts, resolve open GitHub issues on the enrollment priority work, and plan milestones for the remainder of the year. 

Key outcomes included resolving a critical propagation and lollipop counter logic conflict in the enrollment priority specification, assigning reviewers for `draft-ietf-roll-dis-modifications`, and outlining the future path for `draft-ietf-roll-nsa-extension`. Work on MoPs (Modes of Operation) and Capabilities has been officially deferred and removed from active milestones.

## Key Discussion Points

